overview: The user initiated a comprehensive review of their sleep questionnaire
  application to verify adherence to the provided specification. The agent
  conducted an in-depth analysis of the codebase, identifying several areas
  requiring improvement. A detailed plan was then generated, categorizing
  missing features by priority. The agent has since begun implementing this
  plan, successfully integrating a 1-10 severity scale for tiredness, complete
  with dynamic safety warnings in both the questionnaire interface and the
  generated PDF reports. Additionally, the agent implemented explicit detection
  logic for Comorbid Insomnia and Sleep Apnea (COMISA), ensuring this critical
  condition is accurately identified and reported, with appropriate messaging to
  avoid redundancy with individual insomnia and sleep apnea diagnoses.
